        <div class="col-lg-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
          <div class="box">
            <div class="icon"><i class="bi bi-broadcast-pin"></i></div>
            <h4 class="title"><a href="">Plantation Drives</a></h4>
            <p class="description">The Green saviours association has been engaged in tree plantation and
              maintanance activities for over 300 consecutive Sundays since April 2016. The planting Team
              comprises over 50 people from 5 to 75 yearsof age and diverse professional backgrounds. several
              volunteers fromlocal social organisations, educational institutions and commercial establishments
              have been part of our planting activities.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
          <div class="box">
            <div class="icon"><i class="bi bi-archive"></i></div>
            <h4 class="title"><a href="">Green Talks</a></h4>
            <p class="description">One of the best ways to address issues that affect the planet
              and the future is to appeal to the citizens of tomorrow. Taking tales of the planet and
              its magical cycles that are not really part of syllabi might just serve to inspire the next
              generation
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
          <div class="box">
            <div class="icon"><i class="bi bi-tree"></i></i></div>
            <h4 class="title"><a href="">Mini Forests</a></h4>
            <p class="description">The team diversified into dense plantation and forest making since jan 2017
              and focusing on the same as a preferred method of plantation has contructed 15 Mini Forests in and
               around Belagavi.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
          <div class="box">
            <div class="icon"><i class="bi bi-binoculars"></i></div>
            <h4 class="title"><a href="">One Million Greens</a></h4>
            <p class="description">In Jan 2021 the green Saviours associationcommenced project OMG- One million Green as
              part of which the team will be planting a million native trees and plants in the western ghats Region 
              near Belagavi, Karnataka, India.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
